# Laravel Cashier (Stripe)

## When to use

- Integrating Stripe billing into a Laravel application
- Managing subscriptions, single charges, invoices, or Stripe Checkout
- Handling Stripe webhooks, SCA, trials, or coupon/promotion codes
- Configuring the Billable model and Stripe environment variables

## Keywords

`cashier`, `stripe`, `subscription`, `billing`, `invoice`, `checkout`, `webhook`, `trial`, `Billable`, `STRIPE_KEY`, `STRIPE_SECRET`, `laravel/cashier`
